<head>IRON</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">鐵</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>COMMON METAL USED FOR MAKING TOOLS. []</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>GEOGRAPHY 30.</p>
<p>鐵，從戰國起，已作鐵的通稱。</p>
<p>鉅，堅硬的天然優質鐵，生西南瘴海中山石上，狀如紫石英。</p>
<p>鍇，鐵，九江方言詞。</p>
<p>鋼，鐵和碳的合金，鐵中之堅韌者。</p>
        </div>
